addMember(address).notice: Adds a new member to the community cloud.

getMembers().notice: Retrieves the list of community members.

removeMember(address).notice: Removes a member from the community cloud.

storeMessage(string).notice: Stores a message. Only community members can call this.

userdoc.notice: A simple contract simulating a community cloud where only consortium members can store data. Membership is managed by the owner.
